    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aeronautical beacons used to indicate the location of natural or man-made landmarks used by pilots as an aid to navigation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
